11:27.453 --> 11:29.789 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why could this not have been
avoided?

11:29.822 --> 11:36.462 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALINA HUDAK: Well, you know, I
would say to
that we have disease in the
