12:16.069 --> 12:17.070 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ALINA HUDAK: ... the mosquito.

12:17.103 --> 12:18.304 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Pardon me again.

12:18.338 --> 12:21.975 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
